name: SnowdenDAO
description: SnowdenDAO is a collective of cypherpunks fighting for the liberation of Edward Snowden. The DAO aims to raise ETH in return for the $FREEDOM governance token to support Edward Snowden's mission of freedom of speech. The Snowden family have worked closely with the DAO and endorses its efforts to unite cypherpunks all over the world.
